      / <persName>Oleff Laurentss<ex>øn</ex></persName> p<ex>re</ex>st j
        <placeName>Helløff</placeName>
      <persName>Jens Nielss<ex>øn</ex></persName> p<ex>re</ex>st j <placeName>Riisløff</placeName>
