      <persName>Peth<ex>e</ex>r H<ex>er</ex>lugss<ex>øn</ex></persName>
      <persName>Jeppe Sm<ex>et</ex></persName> / <persName>Oleff Krogh</persName> oc <persName>Jens
        Lang</persName> kærleghe m<ex>eth</ex> wor h<ex>er</ex>re /. ♦</p>
            <p n="a#2" xml:space="preserve">Oc ku<ex>n</ex>gøre m<ex>eth</ex> th<ex>e</ex>tte wort opne b<ex>re</ex>ff at aar
      efft<ex>er</ex> wor h<ex>er</ex>r<ex>es</ex> fødelses aar mcdxxxprimo then mandagh nest
