      <persName>Pæth<ex>e</ex>r Areldss<ex>øn</ex></persName> oc h<ex>er</ex>
      <persName>Waldemar</persName> / th<ex>e</ex>n for<hi rend="sup">de</hi> jordh
        <placeName>Huswallen</placeName> / ♦</p>
            <p n="a#5" xml:space="preserve">Oc yth<ex>e</ex>rmer<ex>e</ex> pa th<ex>e</ex>n same tiidh oc pa th<ex>et</ex> same thing /
