        for<hi rend="sup">de</hi> closter / ♦</p>
            <p n="a#6" xml:space="preserve">Hwilket wi hørde oc sowe oc withne m<ex>eth</ex> wor<ex>e</ex> incighle hengde for<ex>e</ex>
